      510.62,
      494.15,
      579.65
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Southern, Uva and Sabaragamuwa provinces and in Kandy and Nuwara-Eliya districts after 2.00 pm. Fairly heavy showers above 50 mm are likely at some places in Ratnapura, Galle and Matara districts.",
